{"tid":1803906,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：香港11月貿易狀況略有好轉 出口降幅低於預期","createTime":"2019-12-30T14:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T14:47:08.000Z","uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8613763fa740d749f7ee389f890739366bd417d","tid":1803906,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"（Bloomberg 30/12）//香港貿易狀況11月略有好轉，進出口降幅均低於預期，貿易赤字有所收窄。<br />\n當月出口較去年同期下降1.4%，至3593億港元（約461億美元），遠好於接受彭博調查的經濟學家下降6.2%的預測中值。進口下滑5.8%至3854億港元，貿易赤字收窄至262億港元。<br />\n香港政府發言人在新聞稿中稱，貿易狀況改善的主要原因是輸往內地的出口因比較基數低而反彈。資料顯示，11月香港對內地出口較去年同期增長5.2%，對亞洲的整體出口增長2.6%。<br />\n11月中國官方採購經理指數(PMI)升至榮枯線50上方，為4月來首次，表明全球第二大經濟體企穩，之後的資料也證實了這一點。香港政府表示，解讀數據時需謹慎。<br />\n港府發言人稱：&ldquo;儘管內地與美國已達成第一階段貿易協定，但環球經濟增長仍有待改善，加上週邊環境仍有多項不確定因素，政府會繼續密切留意有關情況。&rdquo;//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.bbwc.cn/meyfnb.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.bbwc.cn%2Fmeyfnb.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkbV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=ed296fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.bbwc.cn/meyfnb.html</a>"},{"pid":"5de0a9dc136ce3cec2ed659556276cc0579287ef","tid":1803906,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:47:08.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkbV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=3b37d461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkbV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=60c18420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;